SEARCH
Package ComparativeGenomics.ServerHandling

Class Job

java.lang.Object
ComparativeGenomics.ServerHandling.Job
public class Job extends Object
Saves all information related to a submitted job, allowing the data to be downloaded from the server it was run on, and displaying the results.
Author:
franpeters

  • Constructor Details

    • Job

      public Job(ExternalServer server, String name, String ref, String qry, Enzyme enzyme, String pipeline, String status, String qOrg, String rOrg, String rAnnot, String qAnnot)
      Constructor with server, job name, reference and query file names, enzyme, pipeline, status, organisms and annotations files
      Parameters:
      server - the ExternalServer used to run this alignment job
      name - name of the job
      ref - reference genome file path
      qry - query genome file path
      enzyme - Enzyme object of this job
      pipeline - Alignment algorithm for this job
      status - Latest status of the submitted job
      qOrg - query organism species (genus and species required i.e. Homo sapiens)
      rOrg - reference organism species (genus and species required i.e. Homo sapiens)
      rAnnot - file path to the GTF or GFF3 annotation file for reference genome
      qAnnot - file path to the GTF or GFF3 annotation file for query genome
